": 367, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"Evening Standard\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourprivacy notice\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All eyes are on Paris as the2024 Olympics Gamesare fully underway - but as the global sporting elite battle it out for medals to bring home, who is shining in the stands?\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7190344071178153e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All eyes\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024 Olympics Gamesare\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games attract the world's great and good every four years, but it's landing in the birthplace of couture calls for the chicest in recent memory (starting withthe medal trays, courtesy of Louis Vuitton).\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1948_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8921105519261166e-26, \"text\": \"The Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1948_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1948_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.341748900600119e-41, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's great and good every four years\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the birthplace\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"couture\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"recent memory\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"medal trays\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the A-list have turned out.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the A-list\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At theOpening Ceremony, Chrissy Teigen and John Legend - both wearing Vuitton, one of the Games' prominent sponsors - lead arrivals, alongside Ariana Grande, who wore a Glinda-pink, Thom Browne princess gown with Swarovski jewels, and Cynthia Erivo, in an Elphaba-emerald green Vuitton dress; the pair continue their method-dressing promotion of Wicked, which comes in November.\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrissy_Teigen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chrissy Teigen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrissy_Teigen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrissy_Teigen\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swarovski\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7668846532543564e-44, \"text\": \"Swarovski\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swarovski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swarovski\"}, {\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cynthia Erivo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOpening Ceremony\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"John Legend\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"Vuitton\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' prominent sponsors\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"lead arrivals\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"a Glinda-pink\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \", Thom Browne princess gown\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"an Elphaba-emerald green Vuitton dress\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"their method-dressing promotion\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"Wicked\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also there was Serena Williams, in a tomato red Dolce & Gabbana dress, Emma Chamberlain, in archive Ralph Lauren pedal pushers and bar jacket, and Kaia Gerber, who wore a steel-grey mini dress by French designer Marine Serre.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dolce_&_Gabbana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dolce & Gabbana\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q